collections.name: A SEA OF SPACE BY PHILIP BEAVEN
collections.description: Philip Beaven is a multi faceted artist who has explored both visual and performance arts. His early career was in eurythmy creating performances and touring all over Europe and America. These involved developing coloured light experiences to frame the performances. That progressed to theatre, having studied at Central School of Speech and Drama in London, before taking up teaching. Through his engagement with the arts as a Waldorf teacher his interest in expression through colour has developed. The paintings on this website reflect his exploration of how the deeper layers of the soul are shone through by spirit

collections.name: Ager
collections.description:
Only noise and lines—some curved, some jagged—  recreate the trembling pulse of the Earth beneath us.  Every Odyssey, no matter how infinite,  ends with the yearning to claim, or reclaim,  a fragment of soil, a whisper of land—  Ager, waiting to be cultivated.

From the birth of the Universe, 
the first sound was Noise, still echoing, 
etched into the Cosmic Microwave Background, 
a static hymn woven into analog signals, 
a distant murmur of creation itself.

If we could strip the Noise away, 
piece by piece, frequency by frequency, 
would we find Reality reassembled, 
or would we only uncover more noise— 
endless, recursive, governed by unseen algorithms?

Ager emerges. 
A digital terrain, a collective code. 
Each fragment, each token, a seed. 
Together, they form something vast, 
a society written in data and dust, 
an echo of past lands, 
reimagined for futures yet to be claimed.


Press 's' to save the canvas or '2' for 2x and '4' for 4x image resolution in PNG.

collections.name: KAWAII Tennis Art Project

collections.description: The Cylinder Six Collection is Porsche-inspired, blending high-performance automotive design with digital artistry. This collection celebrates automotive craftsmanship, reimagined through modern digital media. Ideal for car enthusiasts and art collectors, the Cylinder Six Collection offers a one-of-a-kind exploration into the fusion of design, technology, and artistry. Each NFT is a tribute to luxury automobiles, bringing a digital future to timeless automotive excellence.

collections.name: Dreamful Horizons
collections.description: Dreamful Horizons is a transcendent NFT collection uniting evocative narratives of liberation, transformation, and the pursuit of boundless dreams. Each artwork invites exploration of symbolic themes—from shattered chains of constraint to footprints leading into uncharted realms, from the rhythmic embrace of ocean tides to majestic peaks of resilience. More than a collection, Dreamful Horizons is an immersive journey through art’s infinite possibilities, inspiring personal triumph and awakening the creative spirit in every observer.
